Colosseum is a disaster management simulator and it's quite difficult to have a setup for the complete room. Not sure how useful this video is considering that.

-With just the Ice Beam Mocktroids take four hits to freeze.
-Remember to spinjump and break spin before hitting the sand. 
-If low on health, freeze the Mocktroids earlier rather than later. 
-Use the walls to guid the Mocktroids for easier freezing. 
-Be especially careful not to offscreen the Mocktroid in the second pit of the room or you'll be stuck down there. 
-Use all tricks in the book to make it. Walljump between a Mocktroid and a wall, downgrab to get on one - whatever it takes.
